101
00:06:36,113 --> 00:06:41,513
-Yes, at times. -Well, very frequently!

102
00:06:41,513 --> 00:06:44,713
Then, you've seen it, haven't you?

103
00:06:44,713 --> 00:06:46,113
What?

104
00:06:46,613 --> 00:06:48,813
"Screaming Hospital"

105
00:06:48,813 --> 00:06:50,513
Go inside that haunted house

106
00:06:50,513 --> 00:06:53,113
