152
00:09:08,513 --> 00:09:10,313
You think so?

153
00:09:17,113 --> 00:09:18,813
That's totally out of this world.

154
00:09:18,813 --> 00:09:20,913
You can say that again.

155
00:09:20,913 --> 00:09:22,613
See.

156
00:09:22,613 --> 00:09:24,413
