158
00:09:26,113 --> 00:09:30,213
If you're that scared, I can escort you inside.

159
00:09:30,213 --> 00:09:33,213
After all, he knows where what gadgets are set.

160
00:09:33,213 --> 00:09:36,013
Okay, please do!

161
00:09:36,013 --> 00:09:38,113
Then, she'll go inside too!

162
00:09:38,113 --> 00:09:40,013
Hey, Sonoko!

163
00:09:40,013 --> 00:09:41,713
Don't worry!

164
00:09:41,713 --> 00:09:43,713
It's only the beginning that's really scary!

165
00:09:43,713 --> 00:09:45,513
Gosh...

166
00:09:57,613 --> 00:09:59,613
"Entrance"

167
00:10:14,713 --> 00:10:17,913
Hey, this is just the beginning.

168
00:10:17,913 --> 00:10:20,313
Don't get lost, sonny!

