176
00:10:44,613 --> 00:10:46,613
and the movie too!

177
00:10:46,613 --> 00:10:49,913
Did that person quit school?

178
00:10:49,913 --> 00:10:52,313
No.

179
00:10:52,313 --> 00:10:55,913
