180
00:10:55,913 --> 00:10:57,813
It was only a month ago.

181
00:10:57,813 --> 00:10:59,113
What?

182
00:10:59,113 --> 00:11:00,713
It seems that he was told by the doctor

183
00:11:00,713 --> 00:11:02,713
