194
00:11:30,813 --> 00:11:33,213
Isn't that right, Tsujiei?

195
00:11:33,213 --> 00:11:34,913
Tsujiei?

196
00:11:34,913 --> 00:11:36,813
Hey.

197
00:11:36,813 --> 00:11:38,713
Where'd he disappear to?

198
00:11:38,713 --> 00:11:42,113
