213
00:12:30,313 --> 00:12:31,913
Yes.

214
00:13:03,213 --> 00:13:05,513
There's nothing to be so surprised about, is there?

215
00:13:05,513 --> 00:13:08,113
Ladies.

216
00:13:11,013 --> 00:13:13,013
That's right.

217
00:13:13,013 --> 00:13:17,213
These are just props.

218
00:13:18,613 --> 00:13:19,813
See!

219
00:13:19,813 --> 00:13:22,313
You guys are too exaggeratedly terrified!

220
00:13:25,813 --> 00:13:28,013
But, Anna's strange.

221
00:13:28,013 --> 00:13:31,413
Yeah. Every time after she ejects blood,

222
00:13:31,413 --> 00:13:35,613
