223
00:13:37,413 --> 00:13:40,513
Hey, Anna. Let's not get lazy!

224
00:13:40,513 --> 00:13:44,313
Weren't you going to show us your awesome death sight?

225
00:13:44,313 --> 00:13:48,013
Hey. Come on, say something! Anna!

226
00:13:49,613 --> 00:13:53,113
Hey. She doesn't seem to be breathing?

227
00:13:53,113 --> 00:13:54,413
Hey, Anna?

228
00:13:54,413 --> 00:13:56,213
Get a hold of yourself, Anna?

229
00:13:56,213 --> 00:13:58,513
Anna?

230
00:13:58,513 --> 00:14:00,613
What? Is something wrong?

231
00:14:00,613 --> 00:14:03,413
The inside of her mouth smells like almonds.

232
00:14:03,413 --> 00:14:06,113
Hey, Anna? Answer me, Anna?

233
00:14:06,113 --> 00:14:07,313
Get out of the way!

234
00:14:08,113 --> 00:14:10,013
I'll take Anna to the hospital.

235
00:14:10,013 --> 00:14:12,413
Don't touch her!

236
00:14:12,413 --> 00:14:15,113
There is smell of almond from inside her mouth!

237
00:14:15,113 --> 00:14:18,413
