238
00:14:18,413 --> 00:14:19,913
Poison?

239
00:14:19,913 --> 00:14:21,813
The smell of almond?

240
00:14:21,813 --> 00:14:24,313
-Really? -Amateurs shouldn't smell it!

241
00:14:24,313 --> 00:14:26,313
The almond smell is caused by the poison

242
00:14:26,313 --> 00:14:28,213
