244
00:14:29,613 --> 00:14:32,613
If you mistakenly sniff it in, you'll die!

245
00:14:32,613 --> 00:14:35,713
I mean, I saw it on a police drama.

246
00:14:35,713 --> 00:14:39,713
The almond smell is not the familiar one of the almond

247
00:14:39,713 --> 00:14:42,513
that is usually sweet and aromatic,

248
00:14:42,513 --> 00:14:45,113
but rather, the sweet sour smell of the almond fruit

249
00:14:45,113 --> 00:14:46,813
and flower before harvest.

250
00:14:46,813 --> 00:14:48,513
Oh.

251
00:14:48,513 --> 00:14:52,713
But, from what it looks like now, Anna's...

252
00:14:52,713 --> 00:14:54,613
committed suicide.

253
00:14:55,771 --> 00:14:58,571
"Screaming Hospital"

254
00:14:58,571 --> 00:15:00,371
Suicide?

255
00:15:00,371 --> 00:15:04,471
Did she drink the poison in front of you all?

256
00:15:04,471 --> 00:15:06,671
Yes, probably...

