258
00:15:09,871 --> 00:15:11,771
Beika University, Senior of

259
00:15:11,771 --> 00:15:15,071
the Literature Department of Performing Fine Arts, Ms. Anna Tadami.

260
00:15:15,071 --> 00:15:17,371
Is that correct?

261
00:15:17,371 --> 00:15:18,971
Yeah.

262
00:15:18,971 --> 00:15:22,371
Oh, well... because of her monster make-up,

263
00:15:22,371 --> 00:15:25,171
the picture of her student ID that we found in her belongings

